Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:05.00,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}溜息に泳ぐ　Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:12.49,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}扉を自分で開けてみることは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:15.24,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}恥ずかしくないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:23.83,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一粒ずつ磨かれた　宝石より誇らしく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:30.93,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}輝いて踊りたい　今宵のWaltz
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:34.29,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shiniest partner for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:37.55,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}my best partner it's you
